<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>LittleInvestors — Teach Kids to Invest Together</title>
  <meta name="description" content="LittleInvestors helps parents teach kids financial literacy through interactive lessons, real stock simulations, and AI-powered guidance. Free to use.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/penny_logo.png">
  <script src="/js/pendo-init.js"></script>
  <style>
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{background:#0a0f1e;color:#fff;overflow-x:hidden}
  
  /* Nav */
  .nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:18px 40px;background:rgba(10,15,30,.8);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
  .nav-brand{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
  .nav-logo{font-size:24px}
  .nav-cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2AA46A,#1b7a4e);color:#fff;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:99px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s ease}
  .nav-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(42,164,106,.4)}

  /* Hero */
  .hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:60px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%,rgba(42,164,106,.15),transparent),radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 50%,rgba(249,166,27,.08),transparent);pointer-events:none}
  .hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;max-width:1100px;width:100%;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1}
  .hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(42,164,106,.15);border:1px solid rgba(42,164,106,.3);color:#34d399;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:99px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px}
  .hero-headline{font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px;letter-spacing:-1px}
  .highlight{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2AA46A,#34d399);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
  .hero-sub{font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:32px}
  .hero-actions{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:36px}
  .btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2AA46A,#1b7a4e);color:#fff;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:14px;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s ease;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(42,164,106,.35)}
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(42,164,106,.5)}
  .btn-secondary{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:#fff;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:14px;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;transition:all .2s ease}
  .btn-secondary:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.14)}
  .hero-stats{display:flex;gap:32px}
  .stat{text-align:left}
  .stat-number{font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#2AA46A;display:block}
  .stat-label{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-weight:500}
  .stat-divider{width:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)}

  /* Phone mockup */
  .phone-wrap{display:flex;justify-content:center;position:relative}
  .phone-mockup{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);border-radius:32px;padding:24px 20px;width:260px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);box-shadow:0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.6),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1);animation:float 4s ease-in-out infinite}
  @keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-12px)}}
  .mock-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:16px}
  .mock-balance{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:16px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
  .mock-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:4px}
  .mock-amount{font-size:32px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-1px}
  .mock-gain{font-size:12px;color:#34d399;margin-top:4px}
  .mock-stock{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
  .mock-green{color:#34d399;font-weight:600}
  .floating-badge{position:absolute;background:rgba(15,32,39,.95);border:1px solid rgba(42,164,106,.3);border-radius:12px;padding:8px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
  .badge-1{top:10%;left:-30px;animation:badgeFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite}
  .badge-2{top:45%;right:-40px;animation:badgeFloat 4s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite}
  .badge-3{bottom:15%;left:-20px;animation:badgeFloat 4s ease-in-out 3s infinite}
  @keyframes badgeFloat{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}50%{transform:translateY(-6px) scale(1.02)}}

  /* Features */
  .features{padding:100px 40px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
  .section-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#2AA46A;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .section-title{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:48px;letter-spacing:-.5px}
  .features-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
  .feature-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:20px;padding:24px;transition:all .3s ease}
  .feature-card:hover{background:rgba(42,164,106,.06);border-color:rgba(42,164,106,.2);transform:translateY(-4px)}
  .feature-icon{font-size:32px;display:block;margin-bottom:14px}
  .feature-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
  .feature-card p{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.6}

  /* Steps */
  .how-it-works{padding:80px 40px;text-align:center;background:rgba(42,164,106,.04);border-top:1px solid rgba(42,164,106,.1);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,164,106,.1)}
  .steps{display:flex;gap:32px;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .step{flex:1;min-width:220px;text-align:left}
  .step-number{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;color:rgba(42,164,106,.3);line-height:1;margin-bottom:12px}
  .step-content h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
  .step-content p{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.6}

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section{padding:100px 40px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .cta-section::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 50% 50%,rgba(42,164,106,.12),transparent);pointer-events:none}
  .cta-content{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto}
  .cta-emoji{font-size:56px;display:block;margin-bottom:20px}
  .cta-content h2{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px);font-weight:900;margin-bottom:12px}
  .cta-content p{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:32px}
  .btn-lg{padding:18px 40px;font-size:18px}

  /* Footer */
  .footer{padding:40px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-size:14px}
  .footer-brand{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px}

  /* Mobile */
  @media(max-width:768px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;gap:40px}
    .hero-stats{justify-content:center}
    .hero-actions{justify-content:center}
    .phone-wrap{display:none}
    .features-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .nav{padding:16px 20px}
    .hero{padding:40px 20px}
    .features,.cta-section{padding:60px 20px}
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-brand"><span class="nav-logo">💰</span> LittleInvestors</div>
  <a href="/home" class="nav-cta">Open App →</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">🌟 Mind the Product Hackathon 2026</div>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Teach your kids to <span class="highlight">invest</span> — together.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">LittleInvestors makes financial literacy fun and engaging. Kids learn through interactive lessons, simulate real stock investments with zero risk, and earn rewards — while parents stay in the loop.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/home" class="btn-primary">Start Learning Free →</a>
        <a href="/courses" class="btn-secondary">Browse Lessons</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">5</span><span class="stat-label">Lessons</span></div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">6</span><span class="stat-label">Real Stocks</span></div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat-number">AI</span><span class="stat-label">Coach</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="phone-wrap">
      <div class="phone-mockup">
        <div class="mock-header"><span>🪙 $800</span><span>🔥 30</span></div>
        <div class="mock-balance">
          <div class="mock-label">Portfolio Value</div>
          <div class="mock-amount">$847.23</div>
          <div class="mock-gain">📈 +$47.23 today</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mock-stock"><span>🍎 AAPL</span><span class="mock-green">+$1.13</span></div>
        <div class="mock-stock"><span>📦 AMZN</span><span class="mock-green">+$4.55</span></div>
        <div class="mock-stock"><span>🏪 WMT</span><span class="mock-green">+$0.51</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="floating-badge badge-1">💡 What is savings?</div>
      <div class="floating-badge badge-2">🎯 Quiz done! +50 XP</div>
      <div class="floating-badge badge-3">💸 Mom sent $50!</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="features" style="width:100%">
  <div class="section-label">Everything you need</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Built for kids. Loved by parents.</h2>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">📚</span><h3>5 Interactive Lessons</h3><p>Video-based lessons on money, saving, spending, risk & investing — designed for ages 8–16.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">📈</span><h3>Real Stock Simulator</h3><p>Invest virtual money in 6 real stocks (Apple, Amazon, Tesla...). See live prices. Zero risk.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">🤖</span><h3>AI Money Coach</h3><p>Ask Penny anything about money. Get instant, kid-friendly answers powered by Google Gemini.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">👨‍👩‍👧</span><h3>Parent Mode</h3><p>Parents send virtual allowances, write notes, and track their child's learning progress.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">🏆</span><h3>Quizzes & Rewards</h3><p>Test knowledge after every lesson. Earn XP, coins, and unlock achievements that motivate.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><span class="feature-icon">🎯</span><h3>Savings Goals</h3><p>Set a savings goal and watch your progress bar fill as you earn coins through learning.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-it-works" style="width:100%">
  <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px">
    <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center">Simple by design</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-number">01</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Parent sets up allowance</h3><p>Parents send virtual allowances from the Family Dashboard — just like a real transfer, but risk-free.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-number">02</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Child learns & invests</h3><p>Kids complete lessons, take quizzes, earn coins & XP, then invest in real companies.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-number">03</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Grow together</h3><p>Track progress, celebrate wins, and build money habits that will last a lifetime.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section" style="width:100%">
  <div class="cta-content">
    <span class="cta-emoji">🚀</span>
    <h2>Ready to raise a financially smart kid?</h2>
    <p>Free to use. No credit card. Start in 30 seconds.</p>
    <a href="/home" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started Free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-brand"><span>💰</span> LittleInvestors</div>
  <p>Built with ❤️ for the Mind the Product Hackathon 2026 · <a href="/home" style="color:#2AA46A">Open App</a></p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
